AI-Powered Real-Time Fish Catch Predictor SmartFishNet is an intelligent, real-time fish catch prediction system designed to assist fishermen in
identifying the best fishing zones.
ğŸ¯ **Goal**: Predict fish catch quantity and species in real-time using satellite + oceanographic data (depth, SST, salinity, etc.)

