#Solution
SmartFishNet provides:

ğŸ¯ AI-based prediction of fish species and expected catch volume (kg)
ğŸ—ºï¸ Interactive maps showing fishing hotspots
ğŸŒ¤ï¸ Weather and tide alerts for safety
ğŸŒ Works online/offline with minimal bandwidth
ğŸ§  Uses real-world and crowdsourced catch data to train models

## ğŸš€ Features
- Predict fish species from location + ocean data
- Real-time catch quantity estimation (kg)
- Trained on synthetic + real marine datasets
- API-based backend for integration with mobile/web
- UI ready for fishermen or fishery departments

